    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='222:249'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-1a' );" name="023-1a" class="pb">[023-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='249:263'>禮記要義卷第二十四　祭義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='263:281'>　一禘有樂嘗無樂然周禮四時皆有樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='281:301'>禘有樂而嘗無樂然周禮四時之祭皆有樂殷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='301:321'>則烝嘗之祭亦有樂故那詩云庸鼔有斁萬舞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='321:341'>有奕下云顧予烝嘗則殷秋冬亦有樂者熊氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='341:361'>云殷秋冬但有管絃之樂又云烝嘗全無樂其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='361:369'>義巳具郊特牲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='369:383'>　二齊之日五思見其所爲齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='383:403'>致齊於内散齊於外齊之日思其居處思其笑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='403:430'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-1b' );" name="023-1b" class="pb">[023-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='430:450'>語思其志意思其所樂思其所嗜齊三日乃見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='450:470'>其所爲齊者注云致齊思此五者也散齊七日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='470:490'>不御不樂不弔耳見所爲齊者思之熟也所嗜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='490:510'>素所欲飲食也春秋傳曰屈到嗜芰正義曰楚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='510:530'>語云屈到嗜芰有疾召其宗老而屬之曰祭我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='530:535'>必以芰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='535:547'>　三祭之日必有見有聞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='547:567'>祭之日入室僾然必有見乎其位周還出戸肅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='567:587'>然必有聞乎其容聲出户而聽愾然必有聞乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='587:614'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-2a' );" name="023-2a" class="pb">[023-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='614:634'>其嘆息之聲注云周還出户謂薦設時也無尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='634:654'>者闔户若食間則有出户而聽之正義曰此一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='654:674'>經明祭之日孝子想念其親入室僾然必有見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='674:696'>乎其位者謂祭之日朝𥘉入廟室時也𥘉入室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='696:716'>隂厭時孝子當想象僾僾髣髴見也詩云愛而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='716:736'>不見見如見親之在神位也故論語云祭如在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='736:756'>周還出户肅然必有聞乎其容聲者謂薦饌時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='756:776'>也出户而聽愾然者謂祭此人爲無尸之時設</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='776:792'>薦巳畢孝子岀户而静聽愾愾然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='792:819'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-2b' );" name="023-2b" class="pb">[023-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='819:831'>　四終身之䘮忌日之謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='831:851'>君子有終身之䘮忌日之謂也忌日不用非不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='851:871'>祥也言夫日志有所至而不敢盡其私也注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='871:891'>忌日親亡之日忌日者不用舉他事如有時日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='891:911'>之禁也祥善也志有所至至於親以此日亡其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='911:918'>哀心如䘮時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='918:928'>　五郷之然後能饗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='928:948'>唯聖人爲能饗帝孝子爲能饗親饗者郷也郷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='948:968'>之然後能饗焉是故孝子臨尸而不怍君牽牲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='968:995'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-3a' );" name="023-3a" class="pb">[023-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='995:1015'>夫人奠盎君獻尸夫人薦豆卿大夫相君命婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1015:1035'>相夫人齊齊乎其敬也愉愉乎其忠也勿勿諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1035:1055'>其欲其饗之也注云謂祭之能使之饗也帝天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1055:1075'>也言中心郷之乃能使其祭見饗也上饗或爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1075:1095'>相色不和曰怍奠盎設盎齊之奠也此時君牽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1095:1115'>牲將薦毛血君獻尸而夫人薦豆謂繹日也儐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1115:1135'>尸主人獻尸主婦自東房薦韭菹醢勿勿猶勉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1135:1155'>勉也慤愛之貌正義曰齊齊乎其敬也者卿大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1155:1175'>夫相君命婦相夫人皆齊齊乎其恭敬齊齊謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1175:1202'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-3b' );" name="023-3b" class="pb">[023-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1202:1221'>整齊之貌故玉藻云廟中齊齊愉愉乎其忠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1221:1241'>也者愉愉和恱之貌忠謂忠心言孝子顔色愉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1241:1261'>愉然和恱盡忠心　勿勿諸其欲其饗之也者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1261:1281'>勿勿猶勉勉也言孝子之心與貌勉勉欲得親</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1281:1291'>之歆饗也其皆語助</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1291:1308'>　六文王之祭明發不寐又從而思之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1308:1328'>文王之祭也事死者如事生思死者如不欲生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1328:1348'>忌日必哀稱諱如見親祀之忠也如見親之所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1348:1368'>愛如欲色然其文王與詩云明發不寐有懷二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1368:1395'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-4a' );" name="023-4a" class="pb">[023-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1395:1415'>人文王之詩也祭之明日明發不寐饗而致之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1415:1435'>又從而思之祭之日樂與哀半饗之必樂巳至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1435:1455'>必哀注云思死者如不欲生言思親之深也如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1455:1475'>欲色者以時人於色厚假以喻之明發不寐謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1475:1495'>夜而至旦也祭之明日謂繹日也言繹之夜不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1495:1515'>寐也二人謂父母容尸侑也正義曰此一節明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1515:1535'>文王祭思親忠敬之甚　思死者如不欲生者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1535:1555'>言文王思念死者意欲隨之而死如似不復欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1555:1575'>生　稱諱如見親者言文王在廟中上不諱下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1575:1602'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-4b' );" name="023-4b" class="pb">[023-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1602:1622'>於祖廟稱親之諱如似見親也王肅解欲色然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1622:1642'>如欲見父母之顔色鄭何得比父母於女色馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1642:1662'>昭申云孔子曰吾未見好德如好色者如此亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1662:1682'>比色於德張融亦云如好色取其甚也於文無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1682:1702'>妨　文王之詩也者此幽王小雅小宛之篇而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1702:1722'>云文王詩也者記者引詩斷章取義且詩人陳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1722:1740'>文王之德以刺幽王亦得爲文王之詩也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1740:1748'>　七孝子之祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1748:1768'>孝子之祭可知也其立之也敬以詘其進之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1768:1795'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-5a' );" name="023-5a" class="pb">[023-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1795:1815'>敬以愉其薦之也敬以欲退而立如將受命巳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1815:1835'>徹而退敬齊之色不絕於靣注云詘充詘形容</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1835:1855'>喜貌也進之謂進血腥也愉顔色和貌也薦之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1855:1869'>謂進熟也欲婉順貌齊謂齊莊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1869:1888'>　八孝子如執玉如奉盈如弗勝如將失之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1888:1908'>孝子如執玉如奉盈洞洞屬屬然如弗勝如將</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1908:1928'>失之嚴威儼恪非所以事親也成人之道也注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1928:1948'>云成人旣冠者然則孝子不失其孺子之心也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1948:1956'>　九諸侯曰霸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1956:1983'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-5b' );" name="023-5b" class="pb">[023-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1983:2003'>云天子衰諸侯興故曰霸者案中候諸侯曰霸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2003:2016'>注云霸把也把天子之事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2016:2031'>　十麗牲毛牛刲取膟膋爓腥祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2031:2051'>祭之日君牽牲穆答君卿大夫序從旣入廟門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2051:2071'>麗于碑卿大夫袒而毛牛尚耳鸞刀以刲取膟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2071:2091'>膋乃退爓祭祭腥而退敬之至也注云祭謂祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2091:2111'>宗廟也穆子姓也答對也序以次第從也序或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2111:2131'>爲豫麗猶繫也毛牛尚耳以耳毛爲上也膟膋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2131:2151'>血與腸間脂也爓祭祭腥祭爓肉腥肉也湯肉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2151:2178'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-6a' );" name="023-6a" class="pb">[023-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2178:2198'>曰爓爓祭祭腥或爲合祭腥泄䐲孰也正義曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2198:2218'>卿大夫序從者卿大夫佐幣士奉芻依次第而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2218:2238'>從君也　旣入廟門麗于碑者麗繫也君牽牲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2238:2258'>入廟門繫著中庭碑也王肅云以紖貫碑中君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2258:2278'>從北待之也鸞刀以刲取膟膋者謂用鸞刀刲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2278:2298'>割牲體又取血及腸間脂血以供薦而膋以供</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2298:2318'>炙肝及爇蕭也案說文及字林云膟血祭膋是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2318:2338'>牛腸間脂也是膟爲血膋爲腸間脂也云爓祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2338:2358'>祭腥祭爓肉腥肉也者旣疊出經文爓祭之事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2358:2385'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-6b' );" name="023-6b" class="pb">[023-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2385:2405'>祭腥之語然後解云謂祭爓肉也腥肉也祭爓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2405:2425'>肉即經之爓祭也云腥肉即經之祭腥也其祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2425:2445'>腥肉爓肉並當朝踐之節此腥肉則禮運云腥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2445:2465'>其爼也爓肉即禮運云孰其殽也此先云爓者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2465:2485'>記者便文耳非先後之次云湯肉曰爓者以鬼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2485:2505'>神異於生雖曰孰殽但湯肉而巳若其小祀則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2505:2525'>煑肉令孰故郊特牲云一獻孰是爓與孰又别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2525:2545'>也云爓祭祭腥或云合祭腥泄䐲孰也者謂爓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2545:2565'>祭祭腥四字禮記他本爲合祭腥泄䐲孰六字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2565:2592'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-7a' );" name="023-7a" class="pb">[023-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2592:2598'>者故云或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2598:2621'><span class='krp-note'>十/乙</span>崔氏祭日月三說皆非　玄冕祭皆用牛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2621:2641'>祭日於東祭月於西以別外内以端其位日出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2641:2661'>於東月生於西注云端正正義曰端正也日爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2661:2681'>陽在外月爲隂在内今祭日於東用朝旦之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2681:2701'>是爲外祭月於西郷夕之時是爲内是以別外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2701:2721'>内以正其位也而崔氏云祭日於壇祭月於坎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2721:2741'>還據上文郊祭之時今謂若是郊祭日與月當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2741:2761'>應同處何得祭日於壇祭月於坎日於東月於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2761:2788'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-7b' );" name="023-7b" class="pb">[023-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2788:2808'>西祭不同處則崔氏說非也崔又云日月有合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2808:2828'>祭之時謂郊祭天而主日配以月其禮大用牛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2828:2848'>各祭之時謂春分朝日秋分夕月其禮小故祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2848:2868'>法用少牢今謂小司徒云小祭祀奉牛牲鄭注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2868:2888'>謂玄冕所祭自玄冕皆用牛也何得用少牢今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2888:2908'>謂祭法日月用少牢鄭云禱祈之祭也崔氏說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2908:2928'>又非崔氏又云迎春之時兼日月者今案諸文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2928:2948'>迎春迎秋無祭日月之文小宗伯云兆五帝於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2948:2968'>四郊四望四類亦如之謂四望四類之祭亦如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2968:2995'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-8a' );" name="023-8a" class="pb">[023-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2995:3015'>五帝在四郊故鄭云兆日於東郊兆月與風師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3015:3035'>於西郊不謂兆五帝之時即祭日月崔氏又非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3035:3049'><span class='krp-note'>十/三</span>致物用以立民紀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3049:3069'>正義致物用以立民紀也者民豐物用則知榮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3069:3085'>辱禮節故至於物用可以立人紀也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3085:3100'><span class='krp-note'>十/四</span>合鬼與神教之至也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3100:3120'>宰我曰吾聞鬼神之名不知其所謂子曰氣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3120:3140'>者神之盛也魄也者鬼之盛也合鬼與神教之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3140:3160'>至也注云氣謂嘘吸岀入者也耳目之聦明爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3160:3187'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-8b' );" name="023-8b" class="pb">[023-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3187:3207'>魄合鬼神而祭之聖人之教致之也正義曰自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3207:3227'>此以下至以祀先生先公敬之至也此一節明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3227:3247'>宰我問鬼神之事夫子答以鬼神魂魄祭祀之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3247:3267'>禮又廣明天子諸侯耕藉及公桑之事今各隨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3267:3287'>文解之　不知其所謂者宰我善問孔子吾唯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3287:3306'>聞鬼神之名不知此鬼神所謂何物爲鬼神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3306:3326'>子曰氣也者神之盛也者此夫子答宰我以神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3326:3345'>名言神是人生存之氣氣者是人之盛極也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3345:3365'>魄也者鬼之盛也者是夫子答鬼神之事言人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3365:3392'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-9a' );" name="023-9a" class="pb">[023-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3392:3412'>形魄者鬼之盛極也　合鬼與神教之至也者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3412:3432'>言人死神上於天鬼降於地聖王合此鬼之與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3432:3452'>神以祭之教之至也是聖王設教致合如此故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3452:3472'>云教之至也　氣謂至之也　正義曰氣謂嘘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3472:3492'>吸出入也者謂在口嘘吸岀入此氣之體無性</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3492:3512'>識也但性識依此氣而生有氣則有識無氣則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3512:3532'>無識則識從氣生性則神岀入也故人之精靈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3532:3552'>而謂之神云耳目之聦明爲魄者魄體也若無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3552:3572'>耳目形體不得爲聦明故云耳目聦明爲魄云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3572:3599'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-9b' );" name="023-9b" class="pb">[023-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3599:3619'>合鬼神而祭聖人之教致之也者人之死其神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3619:3639'>與形體分散各別聖人以生存之時神形和合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3639:3659'>今雖身死聚合鬼神似若生人而祭之是聖人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3659:3671'>設教興致之令其如此也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3671:3684'><span class='krp-note'>十/五</span>昭明焄蒿悽愴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3684:3704'>其氣發揚于上爲昭明焄蒿悽愴此百物之精</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3704:3724'>也神之著也注云焄謂香臭也蒿氣烝出貌也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3724:3744'>上言衆生此言百物明其與人同也不如人貴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3744:3764'>爾蒿或爲藨正義曰此一經申明神也此科釋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3764:3792'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-10a' );" name="023-10a" class="pb">[023-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3792:3812'>人氣爲神言人生時形體與氣合共爲生其死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3812:3832'>則形與氣分其氣之精魂發揚升於上爲昭明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3832:3852'>者言此升上爲神靈光明也　焄蒿悽愴此百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3852:3872'>物之精也者焄謂香臭也言百物之氣或香或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3872:3892'>臭蒿謂烝岀貌言此香臭烝而上出其氣蒿然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3892:3912'>也悽愴者謂此等之氣人聞之情有悽有愴百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3912:3932'>物之精也者人氣揚於上爲昭明百物之精氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3932:3952'>爲焄蒿悽愴人與百物共同但情識爲多故特</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3952:3972'>謂之神此經論人亦因人神言百物也　神之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3972:4000'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-10b' );" name="023-10b" class="pb">[023-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4000:4020'>著也者人氣發揚於上爲昭明是人神之顯著</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4020:4033'><span class='krp-note'>十/六</span>鬼神䰟魄之辨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4033:4053'>因物之情制爲之極明命鬼神以爲黔首則百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4053:4073'>衆以畏萬民以服注云明命猶尊名也尊極於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4073:4093'>鬼神不可復加也黔首謂民也則法也爲民作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4093:4113'>法使民亦事其祖禰鬼神民所畏服正義曰此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4113:4133'>經鬼神本爲民神故下文築爲宫室設爲宗祧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4133:4153'>其實此鬼神亦兼山川五祀百物之屬故禮運</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4153:4173'>云列於鬼神注云謂祖廟山川五祀之屬樂記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4173:4201'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-11a' );" name="023-11a" class="pb">[023-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4201:4221'>云幽則有鬼神注云助天地成物者是百物之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4221:4241'>魄謂之鬼對則精靈爲魂形體爲魄故昭七年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4241:4261'>左傳云人生始化曰魄旣生魄陽曰魂是形爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4261:4281'>魄氣爲魂若散而言之魄亦性識識與魄無異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4281:4301'>故昭二十五年左傳云心之精爽是謂魂魄魂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4301:4321'>魄去之何以能乆又襄二十九年左傳云天奪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4321:4341'>伯有魄又對而言之天曰神地曰祇人曰鬼散</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4341:4350'>而言之通曰鬼神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4350:4365'><span class='krp-note'>十/七</span>報氣以氣報魄以實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4365:4393'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-11b' );" name="023-11b" class="pb">[023-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4393:4413'>二端旣立報以二禮建設朝事燔燎羶薌見以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4413:4433'>蕭光以報氣也此教衆反始也薦黍稷羞肝肺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4433:4453'>首心見間以俠甒加以鬱鬯以報魄也教民相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4453:4473'>愛上下用情禮之至也注云二端旣立謂氣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4473:4493'>魄也更有尊名云鬼神也二禮謂朝事與薦黍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4493:4513'>稷也朝事謂薦血腥時也薦黍稷所謂饋食也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4513:4533'>見及見間皆當爲覸字之誤也羶當爲馨聲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4533:4553'>誤也燔燎馨香覸以蕭光取牲祭脂也光猶氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4553:4573'>也有虞氏祭首夏后氏祭心殷祭肝周祭肺覸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4573:4601'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-12a' );" name="023-12a" class="pb">[023-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4601:4621'>以俠甒謂雜之兩甒醴酒也相愛用情謂此以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4621:4641'>人道祭之也報氣以氣報魄以實各首其類正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4641:4661'>義曰建設朝事燔燎羶薌見以蕭光以報氣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4661:4681'>者此明朝踐報氣之義也朝事謂早朝祭事燔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4681:4701'>燎謂取膟膋燎於爐炭羶謂馨香見以蕭光謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4701:4721'>見覸覸謂雜也光謂氣也謂燔膟膋兼爇蕭蒿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4721:4741'>是雜以蕭氣此等三祭是以報氣也　此教衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4741:4761'>反始也者言此上之祭氣是古昔尚質之義是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4761:4782'>故教衆之以反於𥘉始此上反古復始揔包之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4782:4810'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-12b' );" name="023-12b" class="pb">[023-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4810:4830'>也　薦黍稷羞肝肺首心見間以俠甒加以鬱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4830:4850'>鬯以報魄也者薦黍稷者謂饋孰時薦此黍稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4850:4870'>羞肝肺首心者羞進也謂薦黍稷之時進肝之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4870:4890'>與肺及首之與心殷祭以肝周祭以肺有虞氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4890:4910'>以首夏后氏以心皆謂祭黍稷之時兼此物祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4910:4930'>也故郊特牲云祭黍稷加肺謂周法也見間以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4930:4950'>俠甒者見間讀爲覸亦雜也俠甒謂兩甒醴酒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4950:4969'>言祭黍稷之時雜以兩甒醴酒加以鬱鬯者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4969:4989'>謂薦此黍稷加肝肺之薦更加之以鬱鬯然後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4989:5017'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-13a' );" name="023-13a" class="pb">[023-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5017:5037'>薦黍稷饋孰報魄之時始云加鬱鬯者言非但</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5037:5058'>薦孰是報魄言祭𥘉所加鬱鬯亦是報魄也以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5058:5079'>魄在地下鬱鬯灌地雖是祭𥘉亦是報魄不當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5079:5089'>薦孰之時故云加也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5089:5103'><span class='krp-note'>十/八</span>朝踐饋食皆焫蕭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5103:5123'>案詩生民云取蕭祭脂是取蕭與祭牲之時雜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5123:5143'>燒之一祭之中再度焫蕭朝踐燔膟膋之時亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5143:5163'>有蕭也故郊特牲云取膟膋升首報陽也注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5163:5183'>膟膋腸間脂也與蕭合燒之是朝踐焫蕭也郊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5183:5211'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-13b' );" name="023-13b" class="pb">[023-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5211:5231'>特牲又云旣奠然後焫蕭合羶薌是饋孰焫蕭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5231:5234'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5234:5250'><span class='krp-note'>十/九</span>蠶再浴風戻桑以食之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5250:5270'>大昕之朝君皮弁素積卜三宫之夫人丗婦之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5270:5290'>吉者使入蠶于蠶室奉種浴于川桑于公桑風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5290:5310'>戾以食之注云大昕季春朔日之朝也諸侯夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5310:5330'>人三宫半王后也風戾之者及早涼脆采之風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5330:5350'>戾之使露氣燥乃以食蠶蠶性惡濕正義曰前</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5350:5370'>雖則揔舉天子諸侯此特舉諸侯玄言之　奉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5370:5398'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-14a' );" name="023-14a" class="pb">[023-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5398:5419'>種浴于川者言蠶將生之時而又浴之𥘉於仲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5419:5439'>春巳浴之至此更浴之　風戾以食之者戾乾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5439:5442'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5442:5462'><span class='krp-note'>二/十</span>歳單夫人以副禕受繭少牢禮之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5462:5482'>歳旣單矣丗婦卒蠶奉繭以示于君遂獻繭于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5482:5502'>夫人夫人曰此所以爲君服與遂副禕而受之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5502:5522'>因少牢以禮之注云歳單謂三月月盡之後也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5522:5542'>言歳者蠶歳之大功事畢於此也副禕王后之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5542:5562'>服而云夫人記者容二王之後與禮之禮奉繭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5562:5590'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-14b' );" name="023-14b" class="pb">[023-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5590:5595'>之丗婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5595:5610'><span class='krp-note'>卄/一</span>夫人親繅布于三宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5610:5630'>遂布于三宫夫人丗婦之吉者使繅者以夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5630:5650'>親繅三盆以手振出其緒訖遂布與三宫夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5650:5657'>丗婦之吉者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5657:5673'><span class='krp-note'>卄/二</span>國人稱願有子所謂孝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5673:5693'>君子之所謂孝也者國人稱願然曰幸哉有子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5693:5713'>如此所謂孝也巳者言嘗薦美食但是飬也非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5713:5733'>論孝子言若人將爲孝曰此子百行皆美一國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5733:5761'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-15a' );" name="023-15a" class="pb">[023-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5761:5781'>之人稱楊羡願然曰如此是羡願之云此子父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5781:5801'>母有幸遇哉而有孝子如此所謂孝也巳謂然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5801:5815'>而令人羡願如此乃所謂孝也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5815:5827'><span class='krp-note'>卄/三</span>不虧體辱身</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5827:5847'>不虧其體不辱其身可謂全矣者非直體全又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5847:5867'>須善名得全若能不虧損形體得全不損辱其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5867:5876'>身是善名得全也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5876:5895'><span class='krp-note'>卄/四</span>朝位君臣皆立老臣君揖先退</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5895:5915'>是故朝廷同爵則尚齒七十杖於朝君問則席</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5915:5943'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-15b' );" name="023-15b" class="pb">[023-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5943:5963'>八十不俟朝君問則就之而弟逹乎朝廷矣注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5963:5982'>云同爵上齒老者在上也君問席爲布之席</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5982:6002'>於堂上而與之言凢朝位立於庭魯哀公問於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6002:6022'>孔子命席不俟朝君揖之即退不待朝事畢也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6022:6042'>就之就其家也老而致仕君或不許異其禮而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6042:6062'>巳正義曰知朝位立於庭者案燕禮大射君與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6062:6082'>卿大夫皆立卿大夫立於庭君立於阼階上是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6082:6102'>也卿大夫立於庭北靣君降自阼階南郷爾卿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6102:6122'>卿西靣爾大夫大夫皆少進皆北靣爾謂揖也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6122:6150'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-16a' );" name="023-16a" class="pb">[023-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6150:6170'>於時老臣君揖則退不待朝事畢也則於路寢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6170:6188'>門外日視朝亦揖竟即退不待朝事畢也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6188:6209'><span class='krp-note'>卄/五</span>祀先賢西學在西郊若瞽宗則在國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6209:6229'>祀先賢於西學所以教諸侯之德也者以先賢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6229:6249'>有德故祀之令諸侯尊敬有德故云教諸侯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6249:6269'>德此西學鄭注云周小學在西郊則王制云飬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6269:6289'>庶老於虞庠虞庠在國之西郊是也大司樂云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6289:6309'>凢有道者有德者使教焉死則以爲樂祖祭於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6309:6329'>瞽宗文王丗子又云書在上庠以此知祭先賢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='6329:6357'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-16b' );" name="023-16b" class="pb">[023-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='6357:6377'>所通之經各於所習之學若瞽宗則在國虞庠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='6377:6396'>爲小學者則在西郊今祀先賢則於西郊也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='6396:6416'><span class='krp-note'>卄/六</span>百年者就見八十九十者弗敢過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='6416:6436'>諸侯待于竟天子先見百年者謂天子問此諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='6436:6456'>侯之國内有百年之人天子則先徃就見百年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='6456:6476'>者　八十九十者東行西行者弗敢過者旣未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='6476:6496'>滿百歳不可一一就若天子諸侯因其行次或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='6496:6516'>東行西行至八十九十者或閭里之旁不敢過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='6516:6526'>越而去必徃就見之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='6526:6554'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-17a' );" name="023-17a" class="pb">[023-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='6554:6570'><span class='krp-note'>廿/七</span>郷飲黨正皆有不齒者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='6570:6590'>郷飲酒賔賢能其賔必少其得爵爲卿大夫者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='6590:6610'>必年長於賔故在賔東西靣而不齒若黨正飲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='6610:6630'>酒以正齒位其賔必長故天子諸侯之國三命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='6630:6650'>乃不齒知郷飲酒爵爲卿大夫乃不齒者案郷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='6650:6670'>飲酒云席于賔東公三重大夫再重注云席此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='6670:6690'>二者於賔東尊之不與郷人齒也天子之國三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='6690:6710'>命者乃不齒於諸侯之國爵爲大夫則不齒是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='6710:6730'>大夫坐於上士立於下者謂諸侯之國若天子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='6730:6758'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-17b' );" name="023-17b" class="pb">[023-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='6758:6778'>黨正飲酒一命下士立於下再命中士齒於又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='6778:6793'>族坐於堂上三命上士席於賔東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='6793:6811'><span class='krp-note'>廿/八</span>易抱龜南靣天子衮冕北靣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='6811:6831'>昔者聖人建隂陽天地之情立以爲易易抱龜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='6831:6851'>南靣天子卷冕北靣雖有明知之心必進斷其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='6851:6872'>志焉示不敢專以尊天也善則稱人過則稱巳教</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='6872:6892'>不伐以尊賢也注云立以爲易謂作易易抱龜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='6892:6912'>易官名周禮曰大卜大卜主三兆三易三夢之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='6912:6932'>占正義曰立以爲易者聖人謂伏犧文王之屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='6932:6960'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-18a' );" name="023-18a" class="pb">[023-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='6960:6980'>興建隂陽天地之情仰觀天文俯察地理立此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='6980:7000'>隂陽以作易即今時易也易抱龜南靣天子卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='7000:7020'>冕北靣者立爲占易之官抱龜南靣尊其神明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='7020:7036'>故南靣天子親執卑道服衮冕北靣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='7036:7048'><span class='krp-note'>卄/九</span>祭之日四如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='7048:7068'>祭之日顔色必温行必恐如懼不及愛然其奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='7068:7088'>之也容貌必温身必詘如語焉而未之然宿者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='7088:7108'>皆出其立卑静以正如將弗見然及祭之後陶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='7108:7128'>陶遂遂如將復入然注云如懼不及見其愛者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='7128:7156'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-18b' );" name="023-18b" class="pb">[023-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='7156:7176'>奠之謂酌尊酒奠之及酳之屬也如語焉而未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='7176:7196'>之然如有所以語親而未見答宿者皆岀謂賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='7196:7216'>助祭者事畢出去也如將弗見然祭事畢而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='7216:7236'>知親所在思念之深如不見岀也思念旣深如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='7236:7253'>覩親將復入也陶陶遂遂相隨行之貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='7253:7264'>禮記要義卷第二十四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='7264:7292'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '023-19a' );" name="023-19a" class="pb">[023-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
